  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-b296b8b3-add5-4678-9dd7-4337355c9178\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c4b929fb-7653-45e0-872f-45e3e6528879\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e0eb10e-6412-481a-8182-0d9ea054c7c6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-df0dea1a-472b-4573-a020-de886bbe0546\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>넘버링인쇄, 그리고 후공정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad8f6342-9f4c-4964-aedf-7b6a906378c2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-16b248fd-0321-49aa-85a4-fa8eebd34a8f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">상품권이나 티겟 또는 초대장에 사용되는 넘버링과 다른 후공정을 알아 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-02779ae6-3be4-4773-8dbf-c1186b647d4f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-02779ae6-3be4-4773-8dbf-c1186b647d4f\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjBfOTEg/MDAxNjY2MjYwNjY5NTUx.bkkLdLSAaG6fwP_MFIqOHTcK0a5Ab6s8TLdVfOJBSzkg.i0jGF9cZoVfl6GshShNlhW_OCpb8l1MyuTe4Xre9o3cg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"4134\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2954\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjBfOTEg/MDAxNjY2MjYwNjY5NTUx.bkkLdLSAaG6fwP_MFIqOHTcK0a5Ab6s8TLdVfOJBSzkg.i0jGF9cZoVfl6GshShNlhW_OCpb8l1MyuTe4Xre9o3cg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-10072893-9b08-4f6f-9990-7a43a131be38\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1758b7cb-b149-4d0c-afdb-0b6870aa2308\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6488a07a-e39f-4625-ba58-37ca69d359ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 티겟에서 사용된 후공정 두가지를 알아 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f30921f-6fa8-4732-bf85-61706c941e33\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-40513a4f-5d04-4823-8984-7d56973713b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-cda734b2-8000-4813-a338-d003af783499\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25dfd72b-f1c8-4880-b509-aa45ba9a76cb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f91a0d70-3a57-49fb-942d-e53a4a352f01\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f7f5341c-9c37-43aa-8ad3-ca326cfe27a2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>넘버링인쇄</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e6b01481-b88c-4cb2-9513-8d2200f1e695\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a0024c5-1e9b-4a75-ba9a-7f83aa81b50b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">넘버링인쇄는 인쇄물의 티켓이나 상품권등에 일련번호 또는 난수번호를 입력해서 그 티켓의 고유성을 보장받기 위한 작업입니다. 이 넘버링 작업은 발행한 수량을 확인할 수 있고  티겟이 홍보나 영업용으로 인쇄하는 경우가 많습니다. 넘버링은 번호가 빠지거나 에러가 나면 발행숫자에 심각한 문제가 생길 수 있으므로 하나하나 확인을 하는 경우가 많으며 요즘은 디지털인쇄로 난수등을 인쇄하는 방법이 일반적입니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9f295a0c-fb81-4216-813b-5a7ddd29a22f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-464c0c82-341d-4c45-8df3-8354bef4e7ae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5df5bc2a-0d73-40b0-9b51-b5cb21602201\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-413e59cd-e07d-4cbe-968c-3b64e6de8ba4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">넘버링은 엑셀이나 기타 일련번호 발생하는 프로그램으로 번호를 입력하고 옵셋인쇄를 다 한 후에 마무리 후공정으로 처리하는 경우가 많습니다. 넘버링인쇄는 다음과 같은 제약사항이 있습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-66506f42-45c0-4c68-bb03-fac7bc96ff0e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8f8b7c2a-d9b2-4f09-8eb6-413bb471f4c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-742ff522-66b0-49ea-bcc6-63a024c30c43\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-25e42713-f244-425d-8ee6-dcda4850050c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">넘버링인쇄는 먹, 적등 1도 인쇄가 기본입니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-966c5e20-5573-458e-87c9-5fa046076f6d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df1036cf-e2ad-45c7-9775-475f1d66e78d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">넘버링인쇄의 판형은 전지사이즈나 큰 사이즈로 출력이 어렵습니다. 작은 사이즈로 재단 후 국8절등으로 마무리 인쇄하는 경우가 대부분입니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6e723fc-ba59-46a7-8eef-9a2360f31267\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a164467e-9c77-46cc-9f00-9a153319f639\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하나하나 조아리(정합)를 뽑아 인쇄물을 가공하는 작업을 하므로 단가나 납기등이 비싸질 수 있습니다.</span></p></li></ol><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-380a29ea-f04d-4b9f-b157-4e22bb2a1592\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bf62d12c-d7f5-497a-a770-f38b2a9f93d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-bf62d12c-d7f5-497a-a770-f38b2a9f93d5\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjFfMTcy/MDAxNjY2MzIyNzY5NjI1.TQJFWLfwI-1xxBm_WDXUbXwdQ2bE6jsqWi_ya4VfQU4g.e_2cWXonJ4Igk0mrz8nnE59NCdZjoZObWjrpbe_Ai9Mg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2953\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2954\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjFfMTcy/MDAxNjY2MzIyNzY5NjI1.TQJFWLfwI-1xxBm_WDXUbXwdQ2bE6jsqWi_ya4VfQU4g.e_2cWXonJ4Igk0mrz8nnE59NCdZjoZObWjrpbe_Ai9Mg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8d2cbac3-5c68-4198-8291-267f4555c244\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-64d049b9-80fb-4e14-be1d-d50e48c53568\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2ea1bf42-0596-4b98-94de-35d9354032a6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">넘버링인쇄에서 미싱선은 가장 궁합이 맞는 후공정입니다. 유효번호를 뜯거나 보관하고 확인하는 과정에서 잘 뜯어 보관할 수 있게 만드는 작업을 추가할 수 있습니다. 미싱은 보통 유효번호 있는 부분을 뜯어서 홍보담당자가 확인하는 용도로 작업을 많이 합니다. 미싱은 가로, 세로로 넣을 수 있지만 복수로 넣거나 미싱선이 복잡하고 여러개면 톰슨(도무송)으로 처리될 수도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d439d45a-375a-43f1-a5ff-cf8475b8d848\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18859522-3807-4783-ae4f-76ff4c8751a3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-18859522-3807-4783-ae4f-76ff4c8751a3\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjFfMTI2/MDAxNjY2MzIyMTMxMDE5._ntYCi-zkb6zrjfyV2zUGJQoBxo5F3EwICX-KpWndKUg.tNr1mv0S5voTJ-Zcq3SMwIM1ZkgzrcIjGFRION9OY1gg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2954\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjFfMTI2/MDAxNjY2MzIyMTMxMDE5._ntYCi-zkb6zrjfyV2zUGJQoBxo5F3EwICX-KpWndKUg.tNr1mv0S5voTJ-Zcq3SMwIM1ZkgzrcIjGFRION9OY1gg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f770b7ee-6167-424b-bc9e-11a69e558fc5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d755c1ce-d00d-4cdf-877e-78f84253041f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a409104c-1dc3-4de5-8b62-6ed10f716631\" style=\"color:#555555;\">넘버링인쇄는 난수 혹은 일련번호를 찍어서 관리자가 이 티켓등이 유효한지를 확인하기 위해 많이 합니다. 기본적으로 홍보용으로 티켓이나 홍보인쇄물을 배포시 유효하도록 관리용 숫자를 정해서 홍보하므로 넘버링인쇄를 많이 사용합니다. 추첨이나 복권식의 홍보물에서는 복권실크를 입히는 작업을 추가할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-beecc67f-d463-43ff-8157-b97d5c7dd969\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-494a827a-cf90-44b7-ace1-f90463d4c3bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-494a827a-cf90-44b7-ace1-f90463d4c3bc\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjFfMjI5/MDAxNjY2MzIyNTQ0MDUz.SEhTlC2KhuE-XOueCmlzb2GaMBhnLe_EWHZ4pfWK_j0g.9-ZTegr7MytZl_F5_hisQuX5RejatUzKwy2oAUFXWdkg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2954\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1418\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjFfMjI5/MDAxNjY2MzIyNTQ0MDUz.SEhTlC2KhuE-XOueCmlzb2GaMBhnLe_EWHZ4pfWK_j0g.9-ZTegr7MytZl_F5_hisQuX5RejatUzKwy2oAUFXWdkg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-5dec39da-01ca-42ba-b3c5-d8d3aa4061a3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-585e519e-4ade-486d-97e6-3a6ab61d1aa2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7f8b2d9c-366d-469f-8c95-693f71c3c554\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-690f2001-78e1-45bc-ac66-1e0c28e47f3f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>일련번호 만드는 엑셀</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75c7ff30-0517-4c8f-92f3-a24bda7691e0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-be8a2b6b-43b7-4984-9e3b-329565012850\" style=\"color:#555555;\">넘버링 작업시 일련번호를 만드는 간단한 방법을 소개합니다. 참고사항입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4